        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2325545425" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15323917160488166274">I thought the book was ok. I’m not sure if at another time I would have enjoyed it more but I just couldn’t get totally into it. There were parts that were interesting and parts I just wanted to get through. It’s probably the &quot;it’s me not you&quot; thing I’ve got going here. I am however, finally going to unhaul all three mass market paperbacks and not even continue with the books unless it’s through the library some day. <br/><br/>Mel 🖤🐶🐺🐾</span>
  <span id="freeText15323917160488166274" style="display:none">I thought the book was ok. I’m not sure if at another time I would have enjoyed it more but I just couldn’t get totally into it. There were parts that were interesting and parts I just wanted to get through. It’s probably the "it’s me not you" thing I’ve got going here. I am however, finally going to unhaul all three mass market paperbacks and not even continue with the books unless it’s through the library some day. <br /><br />Mel 🖤🐶🐺🐾</span>
